   Ahhhh, Howling 2. Not really considered a great show, but the credits are
some of the funniest I've ever seen. Sybil Danning was a total knockout back
in the time before commonplace breast implants & cosmetic surgery. Wow.
  Anyway, here's my favourite part of the flick, with Steve Parsons / Babel
performing the club mix of "Howling". I've included an mp3 of it I acquired
somewhere else, and a couple of screenshots of Ms. Danning from the movie.
